---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Romain Missoum - Portfolio">
	<section id="cta" class="container cta-section">
		<div class="cta-content">
			<p class="cta-text">Étudiant en BUT Informatique, j'apprends en faisant — projets académiques, IA locale et tout ce qui me tombe sous la main</p>
			<div class="cta-buttons">
				<a href="Portfolio/about" class="btn btn-primary">En savoir plus →</a>
				<a href="Portfolio/projects" class="btn btn-secondary">Voir mes projets →</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="highlights" class="container highlights">
		<h2>Mes Compétences Clés</h2>
		<div class="highlights-grid">
			<div class="highlight-card">
				<div class="icon">💻</div>
				<h3>Développement Web</h3>
				<p>HTML, CSS et création d'interfaces modernes</p>
			</div>
			<div class="highlight-card">
				<div class="icon">🐍</div>
				<h3>Programmation</h3>
				<p>Python, Java, JavaFX et algorithmes</p>
			</div>
			<div class="highlight-card">
				<div class="icon">💾</div>
				<h3>Bases de données</h3>
				<p>PostgreSQL, MySQL et conception de schémas</p>
			</div>
			<div class="highlight-card">
				<div class="icon">🔧</div>
				<h3>Administration Système</h3>
				<p>Installation et configuration d'OS</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="featured" class="container featured-section">
		<h2>Projet Récent</h2>
		<div class="featured-project">
			<div class="project-content">
				<h3>Zenior — Application web pour aidants familiaux</h3>
				<p>Application web développée en équipe de 5 dans le cadre du BUT2. Gestion de rendez-vous, contacts et tâches pour les aidants. Stack PHP/Symfony, avec Jira pour le suivi agile et respect du RGPD.</p>
				<div class="skills-list">
					<span class="skill-tag">PHP / Symfony</span>
					<span class="skill-tag">SQL</span>
					<span class="skill-tag">JavaScript</span>
					<span class="skill-tag">Jira</span>
					<span class="skill-tag">GitLab</span>
				</div>
				<a href="Portfolio/zenior" class="btn btn-secondary">Voir le projet →</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="cta-bottom" class="container cta-section-bottom">
		<h2>Disponible pour collaborations</h2>
		<p>Actuellement en stage — ouvert aux collaborations ponctuelles, projets et échanges. Contactez-moi via LinkedIn ou GitHub.</p>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.cta-section {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 60px;
	}

	.cta-content {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.1) 0%, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05) 100%);
		padding: 50px 40px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 2px solid rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.3);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
	}

	.cta-text {
		font-size: 1.6em;
		color: var(--primary);
		margin-bottom: 30px;
		font-weight: 500;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 20px;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 14px 32px;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-weight: 600;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 1.05em;
	}

	.btn-primary {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #1d4ed8);
		color: #ffffff;
	}

	.btn-primary:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.4);
	}

	.btn-secondary {
		background: transparent;
		color: var(--primary);
		border: 2px solid var(--primary);
	}

	.btn-secondary:hover {
		background: rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.1);
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		border-color: var(--primary);
		color: var(--primary);
	}

	.highlights {
		margin: 80px 0;
	}

	.highlights-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 25px;
		margin-top: 40px;
	}

	.highlight-card {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.6) 0%, rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.6) 100%);
		padding: 30px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		text-align: center;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		border: 1px solid rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.2);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
	}

	.highlight-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-10px);
		border-color: var(--primary);
		box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.25);
	}

	.highlight-card .icon {
		font-size: 2.5em;
		margin-bottom: 15px;
	}

	.highlight-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.25em;
		margin-bottom: 10px;
		color: var(--dk-accent);
	}

	.highlight-card p {
		color: var(--dk-muted);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.featured-section {
		margin: 80px 0;
	}

	.featured-project {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.1) 0%, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05) 100%);
		padding: 40px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 2px solid rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.3);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.project-content h3 {
		font-size: 1.5em;
		color: var(--primary);
		margin-bottom: 15px;
	}

	.project-content p {
		color: var(--text-2);
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.skills-list {
		display: flex;
		gap: 10px;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		margin-bottom: 25px;
	}

	.skill-tag {
		background: rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.1);
		color: var(--primary);
		padding: 8px 15px;
		border-radius: 20px;
		font-size: 0.9em;
		border: 1px solid rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.3);
	}

	.cta-section-bottom {
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.1) 0%, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05) 100%);
		padding: 60px 40px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 2px solid rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.3);
		margin-bottom: 40px;
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
	}

	.cta-section-bottom h2 {
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.cta-section-bottom p {
		font-size: 1.15em;
		color: var(--text-2);
		margin-bottom: 30px;
		max-width: 600px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.container {
		width: 80%;
		margin: 0 auto;
		max-width: 1200px;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.cta-text {
			font-size: 1.3em;
		}

		.cta-buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
		}

		.btn {
			width: 100%;
		}

		.highlights-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.featured-project {
			padding: 25px;
		}

		.cta-section-bottom {
			padding: 40px 25px;
		}
	}
</style>

